msgstr "If he allows water to escape that has a value of more than one <i lang=\"pli\">māsaka</i> but less than five <i lang=\"pli\">māsakas</i>, he commits a serious offense."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:59.12"
msgid "Māsakaṃ vā ūnamāsakaṃ vā agghanakaṃ udakaṃ nikkhāmeti, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
