#. </p><hr><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:96.1"
msgid "2.1. Vinīta­vatthu­uddāna­gāthā"
msgstr "Case rulings"

#. </h2><div class="uddana"><h5>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:96.2"
msgid ""
msgstr "Mnemonic list"

#. </h5><p><a class="sc" id="92"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.282"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:97.1"
msgid "Rajakehi pañca akkhātā,"
msgstr "Five are told with dyers,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:97.2"
msgid "caturo attharaṇehi ca;"
msgstr "And four with blankets;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:97.3"
msgid "Andhakārena ve pañca,"
msgstr "Five with darkness,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:97.4"
msgid "pañca hāraṇakena ca."
msgstr "And five with a carrier."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="93"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.283"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:98.1"
msgid "Niruttiyā pañca akkhātā,"
msgstr "Five are told with speech,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:98.2"
msgid "vātehi apare duve;"
msgstr "Another two with wind;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:98.3"
msgid "Asambhinne kusāpāto,"
msgstr "Fresh, the dropping of a grass ticket,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: jantaggena → jantāgharena (s1-3) | jantagghena (pts1)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:98.4"
msgid "jantaggena sahā dasa."
msgstr "With the sauna it is ten."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="94"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.284"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:99.1"
msgid "Vighāsehi pañca akkhātā,"
msgstr "Five are told with animal kills,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:99.2"
msgid "pañca ceva amūlakā;"
msgstr "And five without grounds;"

#. <br>
#. VAR: kuramaṃsañca → kūramaṃsañca (s1-3) | kuru-maṃsañ ca (pts1)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:99.3"
msgid "Dubbhikkhe kuramaṃsañca,"
msgstr "During a shortage of food: boiled rice, and meat,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:99.4"
msgid "pūva­sak­kha­li­modakā."
msgstr "Cakes, pastries, confectioneries."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="95"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.285"></a> 
#. VAR: Cha­parik­khā­ra­thavikā → saparik­khā­ra­thavi­kaṃ (bj) | saparik­khā­ra­thavikā (s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:100.1"
msgid "Cha­parik­khā­ra­thavikā,"
msgstr "Six on articles, bag,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:100.2"
msgid "bhisivaṃsā na nikkhame;"
msgstr "Cushion, bamboo, on not coming out;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:100.3"
msgid "Khādanīyañca vissāsaṃ,"
msgstr "And taking food on trust,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:100.4"
msgid "sasaññāyapare duve."
msgstr "Another two on perceiving as one’s own."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="96"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.286"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:101.1"
msgid "Satta nāvaharāmāti,"
msgstr "Seven on “We didn’t take,”"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:101.2"
msgid "satta ceva avāharuṃ;"
msgstr "And seven where they did take;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:101.3"
msgid "Saṃghassa avaharuṃ satta,"
msgstr "Seven where they took from the Order,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:101.4"
msgid "pupphehi apare duve."
msgstr "Another two with flowers."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="97"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.287"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:102.1"
msgid "Tayo ca vuttavādino,"
msgstr "And three on taking messages,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:102.2"
msgid "maṇi tīṇi atikkame;"
msgstr "Three on taking jewels past;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:102.3"
msgid "Sūkarā ca migā macchā,"
msgstr "And pigs, deer, fish,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:102.4"
msgid "yānañcāpi pavattayi."
msgstr "And he set a vehicle in motion."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="98"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.288"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:103.1"
msgid "Duve pesī duve dārū,"
msgstr "Two on a piece, two on wood,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:103.2"
msgid "paṃsukūlaṃ duve dakā;"
msgstr "Discarded, two on water;"

#. <br>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.56"></a>"
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:103.3"
msgid "Anu­pubba­vidhā­nena,"
msgstr "Step by step, by arrangement,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:103.4"
msgid "tadañño na paripūrayi."
msgstr "Another did not amount to it."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="99"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.289"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:104.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyā caturo muṭṭhī,"
msgstr "Four handfuls at Sāvatthī,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:104.2"
msgid "dve vighāsā duve tiṇā;"
msgstr "Two on scraps of meat, two about grass;"

#. <br><a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.94"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:104.3"
msgid "Saṃghassa bhājayuṃ satta,"
msgstr "Seven where they divided the belongings of the Order,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:104.4"
msgid "satta ceva assāmikā."
msgstr "And seven on non-owners."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="100"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.290"></a> 
#. VAR: Dārudakā → dārudakaṃ (bj) | dārūdakā (s2, s3)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:105.1"
msgid "Dārudakā mattikā dve tiṇāni,"
msgstr "Wood, water, clay, two on grass,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: avahāsi seyyaṃ → avahāsiseyyuṃ (bj) | avahāsi theyyaṃ (pts1)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:105.2"
msgid "Saṃghassa satta avahāsi seyyaṃ;"
msgstr "Seven on taking the Order’s bedding;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:105.3"
msgid "Sassāmikaṃ na cāpi nīhareyya,"
msgstr "And one should not take away what has an owner,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:105.4"
msgid "Hareyya sassāmikaṃ tāvakālikaṃ."
msgstr "One may borrow what has an owner."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="101"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.291"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:106.1"
msgid "Campā rājagahe ceva,"
msgstr "Campā, and in Rājagaha,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:106.2"
msgid "vesāliyā ca ajjuko;"
msgstr "And Ajjuka at Vesālī;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:106.3"
msgid "Bārāṇasī ca kosambī,"
msgstr "And Benares, Kosambī,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:106.4"
msgid "sāgalā daḷhikena cāti."
msgstr "And Sāgalā with Dalhika."

#. </p></div><h3>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:107.1"
msgid "2.2. Vinītavatthu"
msgstr "Case details"

#. </h3><p><a class="sc" id="102"></a><a class="pts-cs-empty" id="Bu-Pj.2.7"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="Bu-Pj.2.7.1"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.292"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:108.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena chabbaggiyā bhikkhū raja­kattha­ra­ṇaṃ gantvā rajaka­bhaṇḍi­kaṃ avahariṃsu."
msgstr "On one occasion monks from the group of six went to the dyers’ spread of cloth and took the dyers’ goods."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:108.2"
msgid "Tesaṃ kukkuccaṃ ahosi—"
msgstr "They became remorseful, thinking,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:108.3"
msgid "“bhagavatā sikkhāpadaṃ paññattaṃ."
msgstr "“The Master has laid down a training rule."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:108.4"
msgid "Kacci nu kho mayaṃ pārājikaṃ āpattiṃ āpannā”ti."
msgstr "Could it be that we’ve committed an offense entailing expulsion?”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:108.5"
msgid "Bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ."
msgstr "They informed the Master."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:108.6"
msgid "“Āpattiṃ tumhe, bhikkhave, āpannā pārājikan”ti."
msgstr "“Monks, you have committed an offense entailing expulsion.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:108.7"
msgid "(1)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="103"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="Bu-Pj.2.7.2"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.293"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:109.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena aññataro bhikkhu raja­kattha­ra­ṇaṃ gantvā mahagghaṃ dussaṃ passitvā theyyacittaṃ uppādesi."
msgstr "On one occasion a monk went to the dyers’ spread of cloth, saw a valuable garment, and had the intention to steal it."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:109.2"
msgid "Tassa kukkuccaṃ ahosi—"
msgstr "He became remorseful, thinking,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:109.3"
msgid "“bhagavatā sikkhāpadaṃ paññattaṃ,"
msgstr "“The Master has laid down a training rule."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:109.4"
msgid "kacci nu kho ahaṃ pārājikaṃ āpattiṃ āpanno”ti?"
msgstr "Could it be that I’ve committed an offense entailing expulsion?”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:109.5"
msgid "Bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesi."
msgstr "He informed the Master."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:109.6"
msgid "“Anāpatti, bhikkhu, cittuppāde”ti."
msgstr "“There’s no offense for the arising of a thought.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:109.7"
msgid "(2)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="104"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.294"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:110.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena aññataro bhikkhu raja­kattha­ra­ṇaṃ gantvā mahagghaṃ dussaṃ passitvā theyyacitto āmasi."
msgstr "On one occasion a monk went to the dyers’ spread of cloth, saw a valuable garment, and intending to steal it, he touched it."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:110.2"
msgid "Tassa kukkuccaṃ ahosi … pe …"
msgstr "He became remorseful …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:110.3"
msgid "“anāpatti, bhikkhu, pārājikassa."
msgstr "“There’s no offense entailing expulsion,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:110.4"
msgid "Āpatti dukkaṭassā”ti."
msgstr "but there’s an offense of wrong conduct.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:110.5"
msgid "(3)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="105"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.295"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:111.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena aññataro bhikkhu raja­kattha­ra­ṇaṃ gantvā mahagghaṃ dussaṃ passitvā theyyacitto phandāpesi."
msgstr "On one occasion a monk went to the dyers’ spread of cloth, saw a valuable garment, and intending to steal it, he made it quiver."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:111.2"
msgid "Tassa kukkuccaṃ ahosi … pe …"
msgstr "He became remorseful …"

