msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:132.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena aññataro bhikkhu divā parikkhāraṃ passitvā nimittaṃ akāsi—"
msgstr "On one occasion a monk saw an article during the day, and he took note of it with the thought,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:132.2"
msgid "“rattiṃ avaharissāmī”ti."
msgstr "“I’ll steal it at night.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:132.3"
msgid "So taṃ maññamāno taṃ avahari … pe …"
msgstr "He then took it, thinking it was the one he had seen …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:132.4"
msgid "taṃ maññamāno aññaṃ avahari … pe …"
msgstr "He then took something else, thinking it was the one he had seen …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:132.5"
msgid "aññaṃ maññamāno taṃ avahari … pe …"
msgstr "He then took it, thinking it was something else than what he had seen …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:132.6"
msgid "aññaṃ maññamāno aññaṃ avahari."
msgstr "He then took something else, thinking it was something else than what he had seen."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:132.7"
msgid "Tassa kukkuccaṃ ahosi … pe …"
msgstr "He became remorseful …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:132.8"
