msgid "(58)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="131"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="Bu-Pj.2.7.18"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.321"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:137.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena aññataro bhikkhu vihāre cīvaraṃ avaharitvā—"
msgstr "On one occasion a monk stole a robe in a dwelling."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:137.2"
msgid "“ito nikkhamanto pārājiko bhavissāmī”ti vihārā na nikkhami … pe …"
msgstr "He thought, “If I come out from here, I shall be expelled,” and he remained in that dwelling."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:137.3"
msgid "bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ."
msgstr "They informed the Master."

#. VAR: Nikkhami → nikkhameyya (bj, s1-3, pts1)
#. VAR: nikkhami → nikkhameyya (bj, s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:137.4"
msgid "“Nikkhami vā so, bhikkhave, moghapuriso na vā nikkhami, āpatti pārājikassā”ti."
msgstr "He said, “Whether that foolish man comes out or not, he has committed an offense entailing expulsion.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:137.5"
msgid "(59)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="132"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="Bu-Pj.2.7.19"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.322"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:138.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena dve bhikkhū sahāyakā honti."
msgstr "At one time two monks were friends."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:138.2"
msgid "Eko bhikkhu gāmaṃ piṇḍāya pāvisi."
msgstr "One of them went into the village for almsfood."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:138.3"
msgid "Dutiyo bhikkhu saṃghassa khādanīye bhājīyamāne sahāyakassa bhāgaṃ gahetvā."
msgstr "When food belonging to the Order was being distributed, the second monk took his friend’s portion."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:138.4"
msgid "tassa vissasanto paribhuñji."
msgstr "Taking it on trust, he ate it."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:138.5"
msgid "So jānitvā taṃ codesi—"
msgstr "Finding out about this, the first monk rebuked him, saying,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:138.6"
msgid "“assamaṇosi tvan”ti."
msgstr "“You’re no longer an ascetic.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:138.7"
msgid "Tassa kukkuccaṃ ahosi … pe …"
msgstr "He became remorseful …"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:138.8"
msgid "“kiṃcitto tvaṃ, bhikkhū”ti?"
msgstr "“What was your intention, monk?”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:138.9"
msgid "“Vissāsaggāho ahaṃ, bhagavā”ti."
msgstr "“I took it on trust, Master.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:138.10"
msgid "“Anāpatti, bhikkhu, vissāsaggāhe”ti."
msgstr "“There’s no offense for one who takes on trust.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:138.11"
msgid "(60)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="133"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="Bu-Pj.2.7.20"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.323"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:139.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena sambahulā bhikkhū cīvarakammaṃ karonti."
msgstr "On one occasion a number of monks were making robes."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:139.2"
msgid "Saṃghassa khādanīye bhājīyamāne sabbesaṃ paṭivisā āharitvā upanikkhittā honti."
msgstr "When food belonging to the Order was being distributed, they took their shares and put them aside."

#. <a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.101"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:139.3"
msgid "Aññataro bhikkhu aññatarassa bhikkhuno paṭivisaṃ attano maññamāno paribhuñji."
msgstr "A certain monk, thinking it was his own, ate another monk’s portion."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:139.4"
msgid "So jānitvā taṃ codesi—"
msgstr "When the other monk found out about this, he rebuked him, saying,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:139.5"
msgid "“assamaṇosi tvan”ti."
msgstr "“You’re no longer an ascetic.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:139.6"
msgid "Tassa kukkuccaṃ ahosi … pe …"
msgstr "He became remorseful …"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:139.7"
msgid "“kiṃcitto tvaṃ, bhikkhū”ti?"
msgstr "“What was your intention, monk?”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:139.8"
msgid "“Sakasaññī ahaṃ, bhagavā”ti."
msgstr "“I thought it was my own, Master.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:139.9"
msgid "“Anāpatti, bhikkhu, sakasaññissā”ti."
msgstr "“There’s no offense for one who perceives it as his own.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:139.10"
msgid "(61)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="134"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.324"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:140.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena sambahulā bhikkhū cīvarakammaṃ karonti."
msgstr "On one occasion a number of monks were making robes."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj2:140.2"
